### City API Tests

### Get all cities
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/city
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get city by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/city/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get city by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/city/name/Ho Chi Minh City
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Search cities
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/city/search?q=Ho Chi Minh
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create a new city
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/city
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Da Nang"
}

###

### Update city
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/city/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ho Chi Minh City Updated"
}

###

### Check if city exists
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/city/1/exists
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Check if city name exists
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/city/name-exists?name=Ho Chi Minh City
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Delete city
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/city/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001 